{"tid":940206,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星火聖誕街站。毋忘義士","createTime":"2018-12-13T17:55:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T06:52:20.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"972504f4ad14acba54ebe5c0e2ea4c0606b706f4","tid":940206,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T17:55:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/47684211_2356249301328855_6742035998206590976_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=ca43b459635f7bdc9e960e639859cae5&amp;oe=5CA802EB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F47684211_2356249301328855_6742035998206590976_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3Dca43b459635f7bdc9e960e639859cae5%26oe%3D5CA802EB&h=bdd22d12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨著天氣轉涼，冷風提醒著大家聖誕快到了。同樣的節日，身在獄中的義士們，只得形單影隻，在更加寒冷的鐵窗中渡過&mdash;&mdash;沒有聖誕大餐、燈飾、聖誕樹，當然，也沒有快樂聖誕，沒有朋友舉杯相慶，更沒有出路。<br />\n<br />\n本周六及日和下周六及日，星火同盟抗爭支援將聯同 守望前線 Story Of the FronTiers、匯政衞言 Empowering Hong Kong、馬鞍山人：鍾禮謙 Johnny Chung Lai Him、東九龍社區關注組、葵青連結動力（葵青連動）、North of the Rings 北區動源、天水圍民生關注平台 - TSW New Force、及東涌人Tung Chung Future，於港九多區擺設街站，為在囚義士收集聖誕卡，讓牢房中的他們在這佳節中，知道自己沒有被港人忘記他們的付出。<br />\n<br />\n我們準備在倒數迎接新一年來臨的同時，在囚義士則在數算千天以後重獲自由的一日。獄中最年輕的義士最近自製了日曆，倒數重見天日的一天，而我們可以做的就是讓他們過得好一點。希望大家踴躍到街站填寫聖誕卡，為義士送上一句「聖誕快樂」。"},{"pid":"01da05e73ed791e9c130ff2657af2cd99f0a1e68","tid":940206,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T18:51:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47c9eec9408bd5b4ee9a2f8e8d57aaf482c63086","tid":940206,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T18:51:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d169215d3363aa83c7983d6b446faf5e7bc733d0","tid":940206,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T06:52:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}